                        | I am a 3B Computer Science student from University of Waterloo. I have deep passion in making beautiful products, including websites and software. I love learning new technologies, applying them and extending them. Also I like working in a team, so that I can learn faster and more.
                .col-md-4.text-center
                    img#me(src='dist/img/steven.png', alt='Steven Xu')
                .col-md-4
                    h3 Details
                    p
                        strong Name:
                    p Wen (Steven) Xu
                    p
                        strong Age:
                    p 21
                    p
                        strong Location:
                    p Waterloo, Ontario, Canada

